data.text: @andliebz YASSSSSSSS!!!!! I go for my second on Saturday and was able to help someone get an appointment for Tuesday. So hmu for vaccine help y'all!
@alixandchill @andliebz seconding turbovax! those small postings of ~50 appts are impossible to get but every few days Javits will open up 1k+ at a time, that's your best bet usually
@andliebz i've had good luck on the state site! pick your site (whether or not it has appointments) and then refresh, there are cancellations all the time. lmk if you want help:)
